sentences.sentence: Interleukin-12 (IL-12) is a recently characterized heterodimeric cytokine composed of two subunits.
sentences.translation: 白细胞介素-12 是一种异二聚体细胞因子。

sentences.sentence: One drug that promises to do this is interleukin-7.
sentences.translation: 有一种能达此功效的药物称做白细胞介素-7。

sentences.sentence: One thing's for sure: don't go sticking any interleukin-6 up your nose.
sentences.translation: 可以肯定的一点是，不要往鼻子上喷白细胞介素- 6。
